    "This input mapping context is optimized for KOTOR.ai development",
    "All key bindings follow standard gaming conventions where possible",
    "Developer-specific functions use Ctrl/Shift modifiers to avoid conflicts",
    "F-keys are used for system functions (save, load, photo mode, etc.)",
    "Number keys 1-4 are reserved for dialogue choices",
    "WASD for movement, E for interaction, F for Force powers",
    "Mouse for camera look, Shift for running, Space for jumping",
    "Ctrl+Shift combinations for advanced developer functions",
    "All bindings can be overridden in Blueprint or C++ as needed"
